{"tid":676660,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫做 “初生的我緩慢站起彳亍走向拾荒” ???","createTime":"2018-05-24T14:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T14:28:01.000Z","uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"196670268329c8b1006a5118ad21cba34b942b81","tid":676660,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2005d50a3ca7415bdf6b5edc635fd6fd9bf7371b","tid":676660,"uid":97036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:23:52.000Z","msg":"周耀輝=鬼才"},{"pid":"065748a78fd67957c02ad1b82e0fec5718495a08","tid":676660,"uid":15935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"走向十方 唔係走去做乞衣拾荒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6c1dfcef75f4058474ce83f92647552d69f682","tid":676660,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"新生命來到世界，「初生的我緩慢站起彳亍走向十方」，各人在「十方」的路上有自己的方向，但前進是必然的，正如「經書向前翻/薪火向上燒」般自然不過。人生於世，為證明存在過的痕跡，就是在「與歲月摔角」的年月裡，感受「華麗與沮喪」，當經歷過喜與樂，苦與悲，才不枉人生此行。「華麗」是詞人的創作風格，〈彳亍〉結尾有其簽名式標記，﹝9﹞讓人一看就能猜出作品出自周耀輝之手筆。他的華麗見諸於作品的用字造句，充滿詩意，如「很想在桂花飄下時/去過/看過」、「山和海之間永遠蒼蒼/雲雨蒼蒼」、「很想在雨點崩裂時/去過/聽過/華麗與沮喪」等等，詞人加入不少景色的描寫，營造蒼茫孤寂的世界，表達即使在陌生極端的環境裡，仍要不斷探索前進，感受充滿華麗與沮喪的人生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cantonpopblog.blogspot.hk/2016/03/jerald-jerald-1-2-3-20002001-4-20082011.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcantonpopblog.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F03%2Fjerald-jerald-1-2-3-20002001-4-20082011.html%3Fm%3D1&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8f891acc\" target=\"_blank\">http://cantonpopblog.blogspot.hk/2016/03/jerald-jerald-1-2-3-20002001-4-20082011.html?m=1</a>"}]}